'''''Rise and Fall of Idi Amin,''''', izwi kandi ku izina rya '''''Amin: The Rise and Fall'''''<ref>https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/rise-and-fall-of-idi-amin</ref>, ni filime yerekeye ubuzima bwa  '''''Idi Amin''' mu'' 1981 yayobowe na Sharad Patel ikinwamo na Joseph Olita nka [[Idi Amin Dada|Idi Amin]] . Olita yakinnye kandi nka Amin muri filime ''Mississippi Masala yo'' mu 1991.<ref>https://www.rogerebert.com/reviews/amin-the-rise-and-fall</ref> 

== Umugambi ==
Irasobanura ibikorwa n’ubugizi bwa nabi bitavugwaho rumwe n’uwahoze ari umunyagitugu wa [[Ubugande|Uganda]]<ref>https://www.travelhemispheres.com/tours/idi-amin-dada-actor-succumbs-to-death-in-the-rise-and-fall-of-idi-amin-film.html</ref>, Idi Amin Dada, igihe yazamukaga ku butegetsi mu 1971 kugeza igihe yahiritswe ku butegetsi mu 1979 biturutse ku ntambara ya Uganda na Tanzaniya<ref>https://artsandculture.google.com/entity/rise-and-fall-of-idi-amin/m026mnh2?hl=en</ref> . ''Rise and Fall of Idi Amin'' yari ifatanije [[Ubwongereza|n’Ubwongereza]], [[Kenya]], na [[Nijeriya]], aho amashusho menshi yakorewe muri [[Kenya]],   hashize igihe kitageze ku mwaka Amin avuye kubutegetsi<ref>https://www2.bfi.org.uk/films-tv-people/4ce2b6eb963dd</ref>.. 

== Amateka Yukuri ==
Nubwo yiswe filime ikoreshwa nabi, birasobanutse neza ku byabaye n'amatariki y'ibyabaye byerekanwe<ref>https://www.vprogids.nl/cinema/films/film~431456~the-rise-and-fall-of-idi-amin~.html</ref>, birimo igitero cya Isiraheli, intambara na [[Tanzaniya]], no gufata no gufunga umunyamakuru w’Ubwongereza Denis Hills (wigaragaza muri filime)<ref>https://www.open.edu/openlearncreate/mod/oucontent/view.php?id=162577&section=4.5</ref> . 

== Igisubizo ==
ubwo yasohotse ku rwego mpuzamahanga, amajwi menshi yarahinduwe  kubera amajwi atumvikana neza. <ref>https://everything.explained.today/Rise_and_Fall_of_Idi_Amin/</ref>Filime yatsindiye ibihembo bitanu, harimo umukinnyi mwiza, mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya firime rya Las Vegas. <ref>[https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=M_9MHJ51bUI Obituary: Joseph Olita on playing Idi Amin] at YouTube</ref><ref>https://www.filmoria.co.uk/movie-list/rise-and-fall-of-idi-amin-mv076151</ref>

